Cellebrite

Cellebrite is an Israeli own mobile forensics company. It contains tools used to examined mobile phones, tablets, drones, cloud data, etc.






GrayKey

Graykey is the newcomer to the mobile forensic world. As GrayKey is the newest of these tools. It provides the capability of extracting evidence from encrypted mobile devices. GrayKey can bypass the security passcode, pass phrase, thumb print, and facial recognition on Apple mobile devices. The company has just released a version to bypass the security on Android devices as well. GrayKey is only available to law enforcement agencies. 

https://youtu.be/RbAUPBjKg1o
